Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:08.14,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,3600)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0}so ra no wo to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:21.91,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:32.13,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:37.46,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:42.05,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Come now and remember that kindly voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:55.34,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)}Someone was there singing for you, the happiness they sang about
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:03:05.08,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:09.96,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:15.48,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:25.05,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:36.82,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)}In this gentle light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:51.29,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0}Echoing Sound - Town at Daybreak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.44,0:22:47.51,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:50.30,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.65,0:23:08.78,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:14.75,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:23.59,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:27.72,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just walk it slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:29.41,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.41,0:23:33.70,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just tell me a bit of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:35.02,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:41.03,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:38.06,0:23:41.03,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}I know, you know, little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.03,0:23:46.86,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.77,0:23:46.86,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:53.24,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All these words that there are can't even describe it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:58.99,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.99,0:24:03.63,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:44.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:53.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you're off to Mistral?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:00:54.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard stuff there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:59.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the food is good, and they say the women are lookers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:02.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,About half a year since the truce?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:05.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And with that. Happy I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Grand Ouvert.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.60,0:01:12.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:11.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't beat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:13.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:13.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dammit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:16.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey miss. Awake there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:19.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your share of the booty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:23.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Caramel?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.34,0:01:27.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a fancy thing. It's too kind of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:30.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:31.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:34.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it. Being nice to the bugler means
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:36.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,you hear the retreat calls clearer, so they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:38.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,With the draft gone and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:40.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,it's rare to see new recruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:42.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You volunteer for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:43.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:44.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to learn the trumpet-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:46.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:48.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:51.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! An honest one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:52.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck there, miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:55.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name, private?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:56.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:59.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata Sorami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:12.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a festival in Seize today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:15.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm leaving you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:23.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:27.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your assignment. They call it the "Time-Telling Fortress".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Set a course and walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:30.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:34.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Appointment:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:36.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Kanata Sorami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seize, Trois region.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:41.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You are assigned to Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,General Headquarters of the Armed Forces of the Republic of Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,1320.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:58.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:13.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The town of lakes and glass,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:14.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seize!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:18.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Assignment time is 1500.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:26.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally get to let you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:32.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Bearing: confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:34.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Assignment time: confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:37.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Equipment: confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:39.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward march!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:17.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,G-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:19.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A wonderful sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:25.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,¥10.25.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:36.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pretty doll-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:39.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:42.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A kitten, drunk in the merriment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,was running full-speed into places it shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can't help that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:53.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kittens thrive on what they find in the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:56.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why they're cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:01.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe for stray cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:05.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, it was a pet cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:31.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I found another wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:37.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the girls in the fortress?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now here's something to celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:57.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:58.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:20.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:25.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:29.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:54.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:58.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot? Getting completely caught up in the festivities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going looking like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:02.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... er...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:09.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Gesundheit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:10.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank y-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:18.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:32.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:34.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:40.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It does look like you did quite a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't at least dodge it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:47.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This dye goes away when it dries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:52.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the festival, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:54.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a legend here in Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:58.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A legend? What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of the Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:04.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,protect the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:17.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll add it on. I finished repairing that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:23.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:25.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:31.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:34.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That meddling...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:36.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:39.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Late, late, late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:42.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We even came all the way out here for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:43.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stand at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:50.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a present from your father, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:54.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,D-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:58.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for letting me use your bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:03.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I tend to get lost on the road...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:06.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm thankful that I was able to meet such a wonderful person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:11.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome. But don't get lost up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:26.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You... know the sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:37.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a clear... somewhat familiar sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean like th-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:42.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:43.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:52.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:53.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:56.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you going to die for that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But that bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:02.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,this is how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:12.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:18.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:23.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3\pos(1840,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:28.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1\pos(80,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:30.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:33.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some business to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:34.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:38.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:39.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be important to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:42.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:48.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:55.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward march!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:02.15,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,The Maidens of the Fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:06.86,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:11.33,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,long before the world turned out this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:18.54,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,a winged demon lived at the bottom of this town's valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:23.55,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,The demon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.63,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,spat fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:27.71,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,shook the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:29.76,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,and caused the people suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:37.06,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, it carried off the maidens that lived in the fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:40.60,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,and held them in an underground labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.49,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:51.37,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,the Maidens lost no heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:53.93,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling to each other with golden horns,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:57.05,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,granted to them by an angel,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:58.92,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,they escaped the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:02.84,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,With the aid of a giant spider,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:06.72,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,they defeated the demon and took its head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:11.93,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,When they did, an intense fire sprung from the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:17.10,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,If left alone, the town above would burn to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:21.27,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,To keep the springing fire from the town, the Maidens,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.80,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,each in turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:25.89,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,held the head of the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:30.06,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day, the townspeople cast water upon the flaming head
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:32.49,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,and upon the Maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:36.92,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,After one year, the fire had gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:41.52,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, to console the spirits of the Maidens who saved the town,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:45.00,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}they have celebrated the Water-Casting Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:41.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The new recruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:47.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Commander! It's Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:50.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It does look good on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I was right leaving it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:55.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But we drew straws to de-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.47,0:17:05.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I got lost again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:10.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:21.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when it's fun to get lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:28.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's because you might meet someone new.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:33.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Being all alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:34.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.07,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:40.20,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.24,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:45.31,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:48.02,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,your wish will reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.24,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:50.18,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:52.63,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound will surely echo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely echo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:57.72,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely echo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:02.72,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}and reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:05.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maidens of the Fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:06.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:11.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold the demon, and silence its curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:15.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,May you never need to wake again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:16.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:18.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A golden horn?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The demon can't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:21.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Have they awakened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:23.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:34.05,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:38.22,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone! Hear my sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It reached.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:57.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound will surely echo,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:59.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:04.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and wake up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:06.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Kanata Sorami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:13.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:16.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How long does your brain plan on sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:18.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Time-Telling Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:21.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The garrison for Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:37.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for causing you so much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:44.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:48.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:49.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:52.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But no more of this nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For a bell like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:20.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A trumpet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:24.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why this fortress is called the Time-Telling Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:02.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sound of the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio Kazumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:41.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:45.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be your bugling mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:50.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I place myself in your hands, Master Sergeant Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:51.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:53.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:57.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Commander's policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:59.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no ranks here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:01.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:03.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,then, Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.60,0:22:08.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's start now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:10.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Reveille! Try playing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:30.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's girl isn't very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.82,0:24:14.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(960,404)\c&H020202&\bord0}Next time: First Battle - About a Chair
